author: RTÉ Sport
title: Nash determined to stay put in spite of AFL shutdown
description: Hawthorne's Conor Nash on the challenge of keeping focused as the AFL season enters a period of downtime as a result of the coronavirus.
content:
After just one round of games, the decision was taken to suspend AFL action.
No surprise, you would have to say in the midst of the coronavirus pandemic that has played havoc with the sporting schedule.
